   It's Never Fun, but It's Not Often
   A Dog Bite Is Really a Royal Pain
   ----
   By Ken Wells
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
03/06/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
