<HL> Technology: AT&amp;T Computer Business Gets Big Boost --- Massive Air Force Contract Bolsters Firm in Battle Over Standards for Unix </HL>
<AUTHOR> Janet Guyon (WSJ Staff) </AUTHOR>
<SO> </SO>
<CO> T WANB DEC IBM HON LK ZE CDA TRW </CO>
